CURRICULUM CONTENT ATTRIBUTION
-------------------------------
The files references/curriculum.md and references/frameworks.md contain
teaching notes and framework summaries derived from:

  Cracking the PM Interview
  by Gayle Laakmann McDowell and Jackie Bavaro
  Career Cup, 2013
  ISBN: 978-0984782819

These files contain no verbatim text from the book. They are structured
summaries of publicly described frameworks and interview methodologies,
created as a personal study aid and shared for educational purposes only.

All intellectual credit for the underlying frameworks, interview strategies,
and chapter structure belongs to McDowell & Bavaro. This repository does not
substitute for the book and users are encouraged to purchase it directly.

This content is shared under educational fair use principles. If the authors
or publisher have concerns, please open an issue and it will be addressed
promptly.
